---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const SITE_TITLE = 'Privacy Policy | CC3PO Audit';
const SITE_DESCRIPTION = 'Privacy Policy for CC3PO LLC. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://audit.cc3po.com/privacy" />
</head>
<body>
  <Header />
  
  <section class="privacy-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: April 28, 2026</p>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>CC3PO LLC</strong> ("CC3PO", "we", "us", or "our"), a California limited liability company, collects, uses, shares, and protects your personal information when you use our website audit service and related offerings.</p>
        
        <h2>1. Business Information</h2>
        <p><strong>CC3PO LLC</strong><br>California, United States<br>Email: <a href="mailto:legal@cc3po.com">legal@cc3po.com</a></p>
        
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you submit an audit request or use our services, we collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, company name</li>
          <li><strong>Website Data:</strong> Your website URL and related information</li>
          <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Messages, inquiries, and feedback</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, clicks</li>
          <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, IP address, device type</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Session and persistent cookies</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>3. AI Processing</h2>
        <p>We use AI agents to analyze website data, generate audit reports, and power automated support. AI processing may involve sending data to third-party AI providers. You retain ownership of your original data.</p>
        
        <h2>4. SMS Communications (Twilio)</h2>
        <p>If you provide your phone number:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Consent:</strong> By providing your phone number, you consent to receive SMS communications</li>
          <li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Typically 1-4 messages per month</li>
          <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Reply STOP at any time to unsubscribe</li>
          <li><strong>Help:</strong> Reply HELP for assistance</li>
          <li><strong>Carrier Rates:</strong> Message and data rates may apply</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>5. Email Marketing</h2>
        <p>If you subscribe: we store your email securely, send updates and recommendations, do not sell your email, and you can unsubscribe anytime via the link in every email.</p>
        
        <h2>6. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p>We use cookies for essential functionality, analytics (anonymized where possible), preferences, and marketing measurement.</p>
        
        <h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <table>
          <tr><th>Service</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Data Shared</th></tr>
          <tr><td>Supabase</td><td>Database and authentication</td><td>User data, session data</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Netlify</td><td>Hosting and deployment</td><td>Website traffic, forms</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Stripe</td><td>Payment processing</td><td>Billing (encrypted)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Twilio</td><td>SMS and voice</td><td>Phone numbers, messages</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Vapi</td><td>AI voice agents</td><td>Voice call data, transcripts</td></tr>
          <tr><td>OpenAI / Anthropic</td><td>AI processing</td><td>Messages (for analysis)</td></tr>
        </table>
        
        <h2>8. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
        <p>Account data: active + 2 years. Audit reports: 3 years. Communications: 2 years. Analytics: 14 months. Payment records: 7 years. Request deletion via <a href="mailto:legal@cc3po.com">legal@cc3po.com</a>.</p>
        
        <h2>9. CCPA Compliance</h2>
        <p>California residents have rights to know, delete, and opt-out. <strong>We do not sell personal information.</strong> Email <a href="mailto:legal@cc3po.com">legal@cc3po.com</a> with subject "CCPA Request".</p>
        
        <h2>10. GDPR Compliance</h2>
        <p>For EEA/UK/Switzerland visitors: rights to access, rectification, erasure, portability, restriction, objection, and withdrawal of consent. We use Standard Contractual Clauses for data transfers.</p>
        
        <h2>11. Data Breach Notification</h2>
        <p>We will notify affected users within 72 hours via email. We comply with California and GDPR breach notification requirements.</p>
        
        <h2>12. Security Measures</h2>
        <p>HTTPS/TLS encryption, encrypted storage at rest, access controls, regular security audits, and employee training.</p>
        
        <h2>13. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our services are not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
        
        <h2>14. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy. Changes posted with an updated "Last Updated" date.</p>
        
        <h2>15. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:legal@cc3po.com">legal@cc3po.com</a><br>Website: <a href="https://cc3po.com">cc3po.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
  
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: #0a0a0b;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .privacy-page {
      min-height: 60vh;
      padding: 120px 24px 60px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #4cc9f0);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .last-updated {
      color: #71717a;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .content {
      color: #d4d4d8;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin: 32px 0 12px;
    }
    .content p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .content ul {
      margin-left: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .content li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .content a {
      color: #4cc9f0;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .content a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .content table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 16px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .content th, .content td {
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .content th {
      background: rgba(76, 201, 240, 0.08);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .privacy-page { padding: 100px 16px 40px; }
      h1 { font-size: 28px; }
      .content h2 { font-size: 18px; }
      .content table { font-size: 12px; }
      .content th, .content td { padding: 8px; }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
